deps.context: find_package(qt5 required components core gui widgets)

cpmaddpackage(
      name "${namefromurl}"
      source_dir "${cpm_${cpm_args_name}_source}"
      exclude_from_all "${cpm_args_exclude_from_all}"
      options "${cpm_args_options}"
      source_subdir "${cpm_args_source_subdir}"
      download_only "no"
      force true
    )

cpmaddpackage(
  name googletest
  github_repository google/googletest
  git_tag release-1.11.0
  version 1.11.0
  options
      "install_gtest off"
      "gtest_force_shared_crt on"
)

cpmaddpackage(
      name "${namefromurl}"
      source_dir "${cpm_${cpm_args_name}_source}"
      exclude_from_all "${cpm_args_exclude_from_all}"

      source_subdir "${cpm_args_source_subdir}"

cpmaddpackage(
  name opencv
  
  git_repository https://gitee.com/mirrors/opencv
  git_tag 4.4.0
  version 4.4.0
  git_shallow on
  git_progress on
  options
      "build_tests off"
      "build_perf_tests off"
      "build_examples off"
      "build_opencv_apps off"
      "with_cuda off"
      "build_list core,imgproc,calib3d"
)
